      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single pump specimen used for validation consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Single pump specimen tested per MRL 2 scope. Inter-specimen variability not characterized. Sample representativeness assumed adequate given tight manufacturing tolerances on FDA generic pump geometry."
