    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model meets the requirements for COU1 at MRL 2. All seven assessed factors are reported as meeting their required levels. The assurance level is declared High based on the breadth of validation evidence and consistency of NIH predictions within the 20% acceptance band across all operating conditions. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
